Features

-file selection using Tkinter file dialog
-reading data from UTF-8 text files
-input validation and data cleaning
-filtering invalid entries (names shorter than 3 characters)
-generating a processing report
-saving valid names to a separate file
-automatic creation of a timestamped report file
-basic file and directory management

Concepts used:

-file handling (open, reading/writing files)
-input validation
-string cleaning (strip, lower)
-GUI file selection (tkinter.filedialog)
-working with dates (datetime)
-directory creation (os.makedirs)
-loops and conditionals
-simple reporting system